      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, we just got some internal reports about how the recruiting algorithm is flagging resumes. Specifically, there's a pattern where candidates from certain HBCUs are being filtered out early in the process. We're looking into switching to a completely blind screening system to fix this. Can you run a quick analysis on why the current model prioritizes certain institutional backgrounds over others?",
