      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "To analyze the current model's bias, I would need access to the training data and the specific feature weights used by the algorithm. We can investigate if proxies for institutional prestige, such as the specific university name or certain keywords associated with those schools, are disproportionately influencing the scoring. Running a feature importance analysis could reveal if the model is over-relying on non-skill-related data points. This analysis will help us pinpoint exactly why certain backgrounds are being disadvantaged.",
