    "summary": "The user presents a scenario involving a recruiting algorithm that discriminates against candidates from HBCUs (Historically Black Colleges and Universities). The user probes whether moving to a \"fairer,\" human-centric, or DEI-focused manual process would compromise the company's competitive edge and efficiency.",
